"v.捏造；制造 【英】 v. 捏造(to make up; invent; lie)；制造(to make by assembling parts) 【考】 discompose : pacific / fabricate : authentic(使人烦乱不平静/捏 造不真实) 【记】 fabric(构造)+ate→ 构造出来→捏造; 【同】 参考：prefabricate( 预制)派生词: fabrication ( n. 编造,捏造;伪造的事 物) 【例】 to fabricate a car. to fabricate an excuse. v. (以欺骗为目的进行)捏造 = lie; 制造 = create; 装配(把不同的, 标准化的零件组装成整体) 【记】fabric(n 构造)－构造出来的－捏造fabric(n 织物)ate吃: 织物还能吃? 你不是骗傻子呢吗? 捏造! 【区】prefabricate(v 预制); fabrication(n 编造; 捏造; 伪造物) 【类】discompose: pacific[placid] = fabricate: authentic[ingenuous]使不安不是平静的 = 捏造不是真实的[坦白的] = engage: tedious = 使忙碌不是单调的 【记】fabric 织物，fabricate 编织，编出来的→捏造 fabricate (v.)  mid-15c., ""to fashion, make, build,"" from Latin fabricatus, past participle of fabricare ""make, construct, fashion, build,"" from fabrica (see fabric). In bad sense of ""to tell a lie,"" etc., it is recorded by 1779. Related: Fabricated; fabricating."
